title: Dishwasher Circulation Pump
description: Dishwasher Circulation Pump ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 15 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11772000 Manufacturer Part Number WD26X23258 The Circulation Pump is an OEM part for some GE dishwashers. It is responsible for circulating water throughout the dishwasher. Be sure to use the model number of the appliance to confirm compatibility.

installationInstructions.author: Timothy from CASTLE ROCK, CO
installationInstructions.title: Dishwasher ran but didn't wash
installationInstructions.content: I got lucky and found the diagnostic test instructions tucked inside the washer under the kick plate. From there I ran the tests on each component until I narrowed it down to the pump.  The pump cost me less than local dealers. The install went well. Watched the online videos to make sure I was doing it right. Was actually very easy and saved hundreds over a service call.
